Statistical Significance Testing for Key Findings
=====================================================
Computes chi-square tests and confidence intervals for the main
comparisons in the paper, to confirm observed differences are
statistically significant and not due to chance.

Requires: pip install scipy --break-system-packages (if not installed)
"""

